<h1>Amakozi Technologies heads for Europe</h1>
<h3>Wednesday, 13 Feb 2008</h3>
<p>Amakozi Technologies is proud to announce the opening of it's European subsidiary, Amakozi 
				Technologies BV, in Rotterdam, Netherlands.</p>
				<p>The subsidiary is a joint venture between Amakozi Technologies cc (South Africa), who holds the controlling share, and 
				Corazon IT (Netherlands). Mr Hein Eltink, managing director of <a href="http://www.corazon-it.nl" alt="Corazon IT">Corazon IT</a>,  
				will also assume the duties of managing director of the new subsidiary.</p>
				<p>The subsidiary was created in order to streamline the processes of doing business in the European Union, and obtaining work permits
				for non-EU consultants to work on implementation projects in Europe.</p> 
				<p>Apart from being a "home" for South African consultants who are on lengthy projects or long term secondment in Europe, the new 
				subsidiary will also appoint consultants from within the EU.</p>
				<p>The administration of the entire Amakozi group will be done at the South African head office in Somerset West. The creation of a
				subsidiary in the USA is also envisaged within the next eighteen months.</p>
				
